io.spine.server.storage

Class DefaultColumnMapping

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.spine.server.storage.AbstractColumnMapping<java.lang.Object>
      • io.spine.server.storage.DefaultColumnMapping
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ColumnMapping<java.lang.Object>

    public final class DefaultColumnMapping
extends AbstractColumnMapping<java.lang.Object>
    A default column mapping which stores all values "as-is".

    May be sufficient for in-memory storage implementations and storages that do manual conversion of column values.
